Texts.Chs: 记住：几乎所有的自然物质都可以进行萃取。还请多多实践，这样你才会发现更多有趣的事物。
Texts.Eng: Remember: Almost everything natural can extract, and more besides. Experiment, and you'll find some truly interesting things.

Texts.Chs: ^green;种子^reset;的萃取最好用于有用的^orange;组织培养^reset;。没有它们，你就无法完成一份^orange;DNA样本^reset;，而它对于你的成功来说相当重要。。
Texts.Eng: ^green;Seeds^reset; are best extracted for useful ^orange;Tissue Culture^reset;. Without them you will be unable to complete a ^orange;DNA Sample^reset; which is rather important to your success.
